# =========================================================
# 👽 纯净版 AI 大模型精准分流规则集 (正向增量版)
# 剔除了会导致严重风控的全局 google/youtube 泛域名
# =========================================================

# ====== 1. OpenAI / ChatGPT (去重全量整合) ======
DOMAIN-KEYWORD,openai
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,openai.com
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,chatgpt.com
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,oaistatic.com
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,oaiusercontent.com
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,openaicomcdn.com
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,cdn.openai.com
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,auth0.openai.com
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,chatgpt.livekit.cloud
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,openai.azure.com
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,openaicomapi.trafficmanager.net
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,ios.chat.openai.com
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,android.chat.openai.com

# ====== 2. Anthropic / Claude (全量整合) ======
DOMAIN-KEYWORD,anthropic
DOMAIN-KEYWORD,claude
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,anthropic.com
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,api.anthropic.com
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,claude.ai
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,claudeusercontent.com

# ====== 3. Google Gemini (精准劫持，绝不误伤普通搜索与视频) ======
DOMAIN,gemini.google.com
DOMAIN,bard.google.com
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,generativelanguage.googleapis.com
DOMAIN,proactivebackend-pa.googleapis.com

# ====== 4. xAI / Grok (2026 最新主流 AI) ======
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,x.ai
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,grok.com

# ====== 6. 微软 Copilot ======
DOMAIN,copilot.microsoft.com
DOMAIN,sydney.bing.com

# ====== 7. Perplexity (AI 搜索) ======
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,perplexity.ai

# ====== 8. Midjourney & Discord (AI 绘画全家桶) ======
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,midjourney.com
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,discord.com
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,discordapp.com
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,discordapp.net

# ====== 9. Stability AI (SD 绘画后端) ======
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,stability.ai
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,api.stability.ai

# ====== 10. Groq (极速推理) ======
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,groq.com
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,api.groq.com

# ====== 11. ElevenLabs (主流 AI 语音) ======
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,elevenlabs.io

# ====== 12. YouTube 创作者后台与视频上传 (精准抢先拦截) ======
# 使用 DOMAIN 精准匹配单个主机名，绝不误伤普通的 www.youtube.com 观看流量
DOMAIN,studio.youtube.com
DOMAIN,upload.youtube.com

# ====== 13. Google NotebookLM 专属全家桶 (防 API 漏水) ======
# 主站域名与子域名
DOMAIN,notebooklm.google
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,notebooklm.google

# 核心后端高频通信与数据存取 API (极其重要，删笔记、存盘全靠它们)
DOMAIN,notebooklm-pa.googleapis.com
DOMAIN,content-notebooklm-pa.googleapis.com
DOMAIN,securetoken.googleapis.com
